    <abilitydescription>
      <p>
	Scout is the ability to notice things that are out of
	place in the wilderness.  The character becomes aware of
	any subtle but strange changes in the environment.  
      </p>

      <p>
        <indexentry>Detect Traps<subentry>see Scout (Wilderness)</subentry></indexentry>
        <indexentry>Traps<subentry>see Scout (Wilderness)</subentry></indexentry>
	Scout can be used to detect traps, snares, lures etc in the wilderness.
	In urban environments use the Notice ability, and use a
	Perception Check in other cases.
